    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Add the <strong>meatballs</strong> to a lightly oiled baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until they're browned and cooked through</p><p>Meanwhile, peel and chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Top, tail and dice the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
